558
00:28:47.190 --> 00:28:49.120
Please have a cup!

559
00:28:50.850 --> 00:28:52.460
You should have some, too!

560
00:28:54.190 --> 00:28:56.000
It's clear water!

561
00:28:56.000 --> 00:28:58.340
We bought it with the money we were given!

562
00:29:01.840 --> 00:29:04.050
No, I shouldn't...

563
00:29:04.050 --> 00:29:05.730
Don't worry!

564
00:29:06.890 --> 00:29:11.390
This water's clean, so you
won't get a tummy ache!

565
00:29:11.390 --> 00:29:16.090
Yasu brought you here,
so you must be a good man!

566
00:29:20.520 --> 00:29:22.800
Don't be shy!

567
00:29:22.800 --> 00:29:27.620
Go ahead and drink! Everyone
has the right to have some!

568
00:29:27.620 --> 00:29:29.740
♪ Delicious water! ♪

569
00:29:29.740 --> 00:29:31.740
♪ Clear water! ♪

570
00:29:31.740 --> 00:29:34.080
♪ Delicious water! ♪

571
00:29:34.080 --> 00:29:36.210
♪ Clear water! ♪

572
00:29:36.210 --> 00:29:40.630
♪ Delicious water! Clear water! ♪

573
00:29:40.630 --> 00:29:44.680
♪ Delicious water! Clear water! ♪

574
00:29:44.680 --> 00:29:49.340
♪ Delicious water! Clear water! ♪

575
00:30:02.030 --> 00:30:04.940
Good huh?! It seeps into every
fiber of your being, right?!

576
00:30:05.780 --> 00:30:08.530
There's that scary look again!

577
00:30:10.950 --> 00:30:14.090
Smile, or fortune won't smile on you!

578
00:30:14.790 --> 00:30:18.420
In this country, we call
everyone's smiling face

579
00:30:18.420 --> 00:30:22.420
an Ebisu grin, mister!

580
00:30:22.420 --> 00:30:25.450
That's why this place is called Ebisu!

581
00:30:25.450 --> 00:30:28.550
We won't let poverty get us down!

582
00:30:28.550 --> 00:30:32.560
♪ Crying won't cure your poverty! ♪
♪ So, you just gotta laugh! ♪

583
00:30:32.560 --> 00:30:35.060
♪ You just gotta laugh! ♪

584
00:30:42.020 --> 00:30:45.240
Enough waiting! Let me see them!

585
00:30:45.240 --> 00:30:47.490
Just a moment, my lord!

586
00:30:48.740 --> 00:30:53.240
Oh, yeah! These girls are fabulous! Fabulous!

587
00:30:57.830 --> 00:31:01.990
A-Are you pleased with them, my lord?

588
00:31:01.990 --> 00:31:04.880
They're... gorgeous!

589
00:31:06.200 --> 00:31:10.430
Simply superb! Let's start
the banquet immediately!

590
00:31:10.430 --> 00:31:11.680
Drink!

591
00:31:11.680 --> 00:31:13.300
Dance!

592
