take me with you!

662
00:33:58.620 --> 00:34:00.930
I'll do anything!

663
00:34:00.930 --> 00:34:05.770
If we join forces, we'll be unstoppable!

664
00:34:05.770 --> 00:34:09.540
Shut up already! Why don't
you team up with Jaggy?!

665
00:34:09.540 --> 00:34:11.070
You mean Kid?

666
00:34:11.070 --> 00:34:15.660
No way. His reputation is terrible.

667
00:34:15.660 --> 00:34:21.870
Did you hear he tried to take down Big Mom?!

668
00:34:21.870 --> 00:34:27.110
Rumor has it one of her subordinates—
not her—took his arm,

669
00:34:27.110 --> 00:34:29.840
after which he escaped!

670
00:34:30.880 --> 00:34:34.720
Rumor? It's pathetic to listen
to that kinda crap.

671
00:34:34.970 --> 00:34:41.220
Nah, I heard it from a trusted source, Boss.

672
00:34:44.480 --> 00:34:47.940
Who is this source?

673
00:34:47.940 --> 00:34:52.360
I've never tried to take down Big Mom!

674
00:34:52.360 --> 00:34:55.100
K-K-K-Kid!

675
00:34:55.100 --> 00:34:58.000
I wounded one of her Sweet Commanders,

676
00:34:58.000 --> 00:35:00.700
took what I wanted, and left!

677
00:35:00.700 --> 00:35:03.240
B-B-B-But your arm...

678
00:35:03.240 --> 00:35:09.580
I'd already lost it before that,
in a battle against the Red Hair Pirates.

679
00:35:12.300 --> 00:35:14.150
Any other questions?!

680
00:35:14.150 --> 00:35:14.880
None.

681
00:35:14.880 --> 00:35:20.380
Then, let me tell you something!
You listen up, too, you stupid monkey!

682
00:35:20.380 --> 00:35:21.340
What?!

683
00:35:22.010 --> 00:35:25.900
I'm the one who's gonna take down
Kaido and get the glory!

684
00:35:25.900 --> 00:35:27.880
No, I am!

685
00:35:27.880 --> 00:35:28.770
What?!

686
00:35:38.570 --> 00:35:42.700
Everyone, the Fire Festival is nearly upon us!

687
00:35:42.700 --> 00:35:45.030
Let's consider this party the opening act!

688
00:35:45.030 --> 00:35:48.410
Go ahead and indulge yourselves!

689
00:35:48.410 --> 00:35:51.920
This is Wano!

690
00:35:51.920 --> 00:35:54.340
We may as well be in heaven!

691
00:35:54.340 --> 00:35:57.710
Eat and drink to your heart's content!

692
00:36:06.040 --> 00:36:10.350
They're approaching from
the southeast in a massive ship!

693
00:36:12.020 --> 00:36:14.520
She actually came!

694
00:36:15.200 --> 00:36:17.070
Blast them!

695
00:36:17.070 --> 00:36:19.920
Don't let her enter the country!

696
00:36:19.920 --> 00:36:23.910
But there is a problem...

697
00:36:30.080 --> 00:36:34.920
Carp are pulling their ship
and they're charing ahead!

698
00:36:34.920 --> 00:36:36.600
What?!

699
00:36:36.600 --> 00:36:40.090
How do they know how
to climb the waterfall?!

700
00:36:40.090 --> 00:36:46.180
Well, the Big Mom Pirates are
known for gathering good intel.

701
00:36:46.180 --> 00:36:49.100
Shut it! I don't care!

702
00:36:49.100 --> 00:36:51.890
We knew they were coming!

703
00:36:51.890 --> 00:36:54.190
Just sink them already!

704
00:37:00.200 --> 00:37:07.620
That old bag! I'm sure she
remembers that I warned her...

705
00:37:07.620 --> 00:37:12.830
I'll kill you if you come here, Linlin!

706
00:38:46.890 --> 00:38:50.870
I won't let you get away, Straw Hat...
